data.description: Picture a charming country house nestled on 5.7 acres of picturesque land. This home has undergone a complete remodel, exuding an ideal blend of classical and modern aesthetics. With three cozy bedrooms and one beautifully designed bathroom, the interior boasts a sense of comfort and luxury. Aside from being all electric, this home is also upgraded with a updated HVAC, water heater, windows, modern appliances, maple cabinets, updated tile, and quartz countertops. The real highlight, though, is the breathtaking panoramic views surrounding the property. Moreover, the garage/shop measures 40x30 with two garage doors. In addition to being insulated and having 200 amp electric and 220v outlets, it has concrete floors, is plumbed for a full bathroom, and has a separate shop/work area with a wood-burning heater. The home has a wood deck and a concrete patio that would be perfect for grilling out and admiring the countryside. There are many mature oak trees and wildlife to enjoy.  It's an idyllic retreat where you can savor nature's tranquility while enjoying modern comforts of an elegantly updated home.
